To perform the tasks you mentioned in Linux, you can use the following commands:

    Create a group:

sudo groupadd mygroup

Create users:

sudo adduser user1
sudo adduser user2

Add users to the group:

sudo usermod -aG mygroup user1
sudo usermod -aG mygroup user2

Make user1 the group moderator (add user1 to sudoers):

sudo usermod -aG sudo user1

Delete the group:

sudo groupdel mygroup

Delete the users (user1 and user2):

sudo userdel user1
sudo userdel user2


List all users:

getent passwd

List all groups:

csharp

getent group
